extends index
block content 

  h3 Enter your first emergency contact.
  p You'll have a chance to add up to two more emergency contacts once you register.
  form(name="emergency-contacts" method="post" action="/register/contacts")
    label(for="name") Name
    input.deep-purple.darken-2(name="name" type="text" required)
    label.deep-purple.darken-2(for="phone_number") Phone Number
    input(name="phone_number" type="tel" required) 
    input.btn.deep-purple.darken-2(type="submit" value="Add")
